property.description: Detached 1 family Colonial with beautiful attached backyard. New wood floors throughout. First floor includes oversized and sunlit livingroom with bay window, leading to formal dining room, large eat-in-kitchen with new stainless steel appliances plus bonus pantry, 1/2 bath and door to backyard. 2nd floor features master bedroom plus 2 additional bedrooms, newly renovated custom bathroom with designer tiles and pull-down staircase to attic. Brand new basement with gorgeous porcelain laminate floors, new washer/dryer and 2 year-old furnace. 1 car garage, private driveway. Close to all shopping, restaurants, transportation, and schools.
